Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see what was going on outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, this floor is occupied by bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hardly feel like drinking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For those holding their breath, waiting\Nimpatiently for their prey in this heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:01:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to treat them to some hot, bitter coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers dance to the piano's rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two people face-to-face is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth of the bombing case and the fate of Akai's ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to solve the mystery\Nof the weekly red T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to Beika Department Store,\Nonly to end up encountering a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whose body was strapped with bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed that a masked man put the bombs on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And demanded that the sender of the T-shirts,\Nsupposedly still on the floor, to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We learned that the thirteen red T-shirts\Nwere bought every Sunday at 12:28...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the clerk claimed she couldn't remember who bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the strange creases in the red T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I discovered that a disaster which claimed\Nthe life of an alpinist over ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has everything to do with this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a bomb next to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't allow the bombs to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bomber...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "ordinary citizen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When 12:28 came around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody had come to buy the shirt, so you thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This must be a trap set by the sender in order to lure me here."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you thought of a way to smoke that pestering sender out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would he smoke them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the sender knows his address...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender likely knows his face too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he strapped himself with bombs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And claimed, "If we don't find the sender, they'll explode"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought the sender would appear and say it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:05:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have to employ such a tiresome\Nmethod to uncover the identity of the sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the receipts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how customers try...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way they are guaranteed to get receipts at precisely 12:28.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could request the receipt to be rung up on that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they might get what they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then the sales personnel would\Nremember such an eccentric customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, no one remembers any customers like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means our sender is the one who made the receipts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's the cashier of the fitness\Nsection who handles these red underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the cash register for that section is in a small back room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No customers or other employees could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, you could make 12:28 receipts without arousing suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:06:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that the sender and recipient are acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, the recipient still couldn't locate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's further proof that the sender was you, who\Nhad been hiding in that small room all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Mai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Maruoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, Fukunishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father, who you killed on those\Nsnowy mountains thirteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the daughter of Maruoka Daisaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So will you stop calling me "chan" so casually!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he died in that avalanche...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sudden avalanche was in your favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the police didn't investigate further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wrote it off as a simple disaster case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, thirteen years ago, on Sunday, December 28th...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The morning before my father went with you to climb that mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wrote about it in his journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that, should you see the magnificent\Nscenery of a summit even once...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might clean up your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The charges of corruption against my father surfaced after his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the company's embezzlement...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you who placed all the blame on your boss - my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Mai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, this woman is the one who set me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Release my son already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it you who ordered me to do all of this in this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I have your son."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you want him back, strap the enclosed bombs to yourself..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Then take the remaining bombs to Beika Department\NStore and occupy the floor of the fitness section..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And shriek that the sender must be found or you will be killed."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:08:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When I am satisfied laughing at the scene, I shall return your son."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know nothing about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My son's been missing since last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, return my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that was your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is at a disadvantage because she really\Nhad been sending those red shirts every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the same, it'd be in your favor to claim that, should it not have\Nbeen for the letter, you wouldn't have caused this bomb frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you faked that threatening letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to deepen the guilt of the sender and punish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unbeknownst to you, Seta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} holds the decisive evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which proves you were her father's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Decisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible... such a thing doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:09:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the thirteen red underwear Seta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, by folding along the creases in those shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get something resembling flag signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flag signals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the method of waving red and white\Nflags with both hands to communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and by reading them in the order they were sent you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:19.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,U
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:19.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,U
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:21.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:21.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,TA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:24.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,TA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:25.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:25.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:27.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,MI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.08,Character Card,,0,0,0,,MI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:30.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,TA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:30.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,TA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,YO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:32.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,YO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I saw you burying it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it about the dead body's burial place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the snowstorm was so strong\Nthat you couldn't even open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, even if someone other than me was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It'd still be impossible for them to see the\Nplace where I buried the body," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Maruoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s journal, it was\Nthe first time you climbed a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A novice like you wouldn't be able to travel far from\Nthe mountain cabin in a snowstorm to bury a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, if we dig near the cabin on that mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one you killed and buried thirteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of an alpinist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you were confident that no one saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there really was a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did your son really disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he just ran away like usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted my son to enter a famous elementary\Nschool so bad that I embezzled from the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I even killed my boss who reprimanded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in the end, my son ran away from home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, someone call the police to take\NSeta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and this man to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also let the customers know that the bombs in the bags are fakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And are only capable of producing smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although it looks like the SWAT team\NSeta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called for is already nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called them and said that the bombs are\Nprobably fake, so go ahead and arrest him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Dad, how did you know that the bombs were fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were traces of lipstick on his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the bombs he strapped to himself were real...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be unlikely for him to have boarded a crowded train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that, my investigation on your behalf has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you already figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I was the client who changed her voice and called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I only wanted you to reveal the meaning\Nof those flag signals that I learned from my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to see what expression that man would make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never expected him to confess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was really impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With just that little hint...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You realized it was about the snowy\Nmountain disaster on December 28th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to think you had that boy check on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flag signaling is used where verbal communication\Nisn't possible, such as on the sea or in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the meaning of the message was "I saw you burying it"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be the mountains rather than the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the receipts torn unnaturally on the right side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suggested snowy mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the color red on the underwear suggests murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One would disguise a murder on snowy\Nmountains as a disastrous accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since disasters aren't registered with the unit of minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "12:28" on the receipts was\Nlikely referring to December 28th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what was written.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a mail I received a while ago from someone I don't know, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what happened to the bomb case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mail from someone unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth sent this mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I can say for sure is that the sender of this mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was definitely on this floor a few moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that the one who sent\Nthis mail was a really great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You must feel hot, but keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Dad was talking while reading this mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the fact that I, the sender, am the daughter of the alpinist\Nwho was killed thirteen years ago in those snowy mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was unmentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard about that from Detective Mouri, right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you didn't call me "Seta" as it is on my nameplate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But by my maiden name, "Maruoka".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when I went into your office...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I'd borrow your PC to look up a snowy\Nmountain disaster case from December 28th.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, you didn't seem surprised by that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I figured you were the client who requested the\Ninvestigation and were somehow associated with that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the deceased Maruoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a picture with his daughter in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you were wearing a wedding ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured you got married and changed your surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of that was stuff Uncle Kogoro told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, it was exactly as I deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:33.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,There is only one truth, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected from Sleeping Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one who sent this message was also a good detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything except that one thing was very accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could they still be on this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe they'll show up if I send a "thank you" reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the wording, they don't\Nseem to want to get involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but did you get a\N"thank you" mail just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, did you make these deductions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I have no idea about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this mail came from your cell phone, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably sent by that guy who picked up my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was wearing a black cap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his right cheek had a burn mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is that man!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took the escalator when it started moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he probably went downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're looking for the same person I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like this place really is dangerous, just like that message warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That message"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The message Shuu left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, while I was away from my seat at the basement cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He discreetly wrote it on the back of my coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why is it dangerous here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bombing case is already solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Near the window of the hotel across the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone resembling a sniper...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a black Porsche 356A parked below.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could they have discovered Shuu's still alive and plan to finish him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Shuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't, Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're targeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we share a fifty-fifty responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're also at fault for not paying attention to your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems as if you're searching for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Shuu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's him all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the left side of the front entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right next to your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want confirmation, make it fast, Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My finger on the trigger is itching in excitement so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could go off at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai Shuuichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vermouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get authorization from that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our boss is cautious as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knocking on and even breaking a\Nstone bridge just to test its sturdiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the hold up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fucking looked at me and laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I kill him or do I not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Partner, this is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The customers are rushing back into the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did he go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The customers are speeding up, and my aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't she dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's carrying a rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they filming a movie or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're pulling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inform Korn as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what do you mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gi—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always doing as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard irritates me as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One who you would wish only existed in novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A private eye like Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry and hand over that gift certificate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll give us 10,000 yen worth, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're issuing gift certificates to all customers\Nas an apology for the bomb commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kid with glasses raced around and said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never heard anything about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't give us that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took all the trouble coming back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, a gift certificate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say it was a smart method...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in order to remove the customers from\Nharm's way, you had no choice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had some business at Teito, Bank next to this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I was done there and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw you guys and tried to catch up to greet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I got caught up in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For starters, he lost his apartment in a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now he's temporarily staying at Shin'ichi's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's Okiya Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a grad student.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} removing the customers from harm's way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing worth asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:23:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a trivial story about a pack of\Nstupid wolves who lost their easy prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't Teito Bank rather far away from where you're living?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you have an account in such a far place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I went to that bank for some other business.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other business?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.65,0:23:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a robbery case in that bank before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone I once knew happened to appear in the\Nvideo they showed in the follow-up news report.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I went there, hoping that he might use that bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he uses it, I thought he might also live around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I would've gotten lucky and met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, does that mean you couldn't find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I happened to see him on the floor from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it seems he wasn't who I\Nthought he was, so I didn't talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've known his face for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stalker, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zombie...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.13,0:24:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is self defense, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.91,0:24:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.07,0:24:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strawberry
